  "name": "RPlog_Imperial_Awards_Ceremony",
  "title": "The Conqueror Award Ceremony",
  "summary": "At the Hotel Imperial on Selene, Danik Kreldin and the event organizer Lieutenant Lauranne Tremichall host the first award ceremony in years for the crew of the Conqueror, attended by Warlord Malign himself. To the Imperial March, Malign enters and takes his seat as Danik presents medals from the lowest ranks upward, decorating the eager young sniper Sergeant Sandor Woden and the gratified Lauranne among many others. Malign personally awards Danik the Order of Liberation for his loyalty, making him the most decorated officer present. Over dinner the attendees mingle: Sandor warms to the occasion and quietly confirms with Danik that he has received payment for a past job, Lauranne and Sandor strike up a friendly conversation, and the harried Commander Lanil collects his own ribbons. The evening winds down convivially, with Danik departing for the Conqueror and leaving Lanil to supervise the rest.",
